OL,3,CProtesters gather outside City Hall as
OL,4,Callotment price hike agreed
OL,6,FProposals to increase the cost of
OL,7,Frenting an allotment in Bristol have
OL,8,Fbeen approved at a council meeting
OL,9,Fthis evening.
OL,11,FCampaigners have actively opposed the
OL,12,Fplans which will see fees more than
OL,13,Fdouble for some plots but the council
OL,14,Fsays the allotments will still be
OL,15,Fheavily subsidised.
OL,17,FBristol City Council has been hearing
OL,18,Fcampaigners make their cases against
OL,19,Fthe proposed rises.
