OL,3,CProtesters gather outside City Hall as
OL,4,Callotment price hike agreed
OL,6,FUnder the new proposals, which have
OL,7,Fbeen rubber stamped, allotment rental
OL,8,Fprices in Bristol are to more than
OL,9,Fdouble by 2026 as part of a new
OL,10,Fstrategy to address waiting lists.
OL,12,FUpdates to follow.
OL,14,FBristol Mayor Marvin Rees told the
OL,15,Fmeeting it was their responsibility to
OL,16,Fpass a balanced budget.
