OL,3,CProtesters gather outside City Hall as
OL,4,Callotment price hike agreed
OL,6,FCouncillor Ellie King, the Cabinet
OL,7,FMember with responsibility for Public
OL,8,FHealth and Communities, said: "The
OL,9,Fallotment service is in decline, going
OL,10,Fseverely downhill. We want a good
OL,11,Fquality service and this will pay for
OL,12,Fan additional officer and maintenance."
OL,14,FThe meeting also heard that many
OL,15,Fpeople faced long waits for an
OL,16,Fallotment and the council wants to
OL,17,Fclear overgrown plots and speed up the
OL,18,Fprocess.
