OL,3,CProtesters gather outside City Hall as
OL,4,Callotment price hike agreed
OL,6,FAfter the decision was reached
OL,7,Fallotment holder Holly Wyatt said:
OL,8,F"I'm very disappointed the council has
OL,9,Fdone this exactly as proposed.
OL,11,F"More than 75 per-cent of respondents
OL,12,Fto their consultation either disagreed
OL,13,For strongly disagreed with the
OL,14,Fproposals which the council has
OL,15,Fcompletely ignored.
OL,17,F"Our petition has reached 6,500 people
OL,18,Fwhich the council has also ignored."
